{"tid":2162740,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Trans科 求教","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T18:07:42.000Z","uid":366025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5bea13e94fecc7bc34bb939fc9131a8ef4c3ec55","tid":2162740,"uid":366025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"已經諗好咗 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想趕喺開學前轉<br />\n而家就先等聽日appeal結果先<br />\n(利申兩科都爆分<br />\n所以應該有得改choice就轉到)<br />\n如果appeal唔得就要柒啲搵department office<br />\n想問下我係咪填form+寫封formal letter去個department or else where就ok?<br />\n同埋成功機會大唔大?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a774440d6e4c77b0728237f7a257cc14ac4dd6d8","tid":2162740,"uid":366025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed76baaa7d7b6644e881abfe30936f1d66f483c4","tid":2162740,"uid":346958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但樓主你唔想啲數咁深入？"},{"pid":"3785ba6fba6f6e0d387b89955a6e7b7df8d44865","tid":2162740,"uid":366025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed76baaa7d7b6644e881abfe30936f1d66f483c4","tid":2162740,"uid":346958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但樓主你唔想啲數咁深入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"一嚟ecof就業好啲<br />\n我知maec 讀咗pg之後都好好環境<br />\n但我唔肯定自己係咪真係想讀/讀到pg<br />\n二嚟ecof好似讀得開心啲<br />\n有多啲ulife/exchange咁<br />\n啲人講到maec好chur咁<br />\n三嚟我對數嘅興趣唔及econ<br />\n好似話maec啲數好多喺ug econ都用唔着<br />\n既然係咁我讀ecof專心讀econ好似好啲"},{"pid":"7cfd33adc1c44cb8e8869deb1df3ca74f2551f62","tid":2162740,"uid":366025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-1